message:
Anyone know if it's possible to visualize Urban Maps in Google maps or any alternative? Suggest please Online GIS service that can be used.

Mohammad Tayseer

data.message: What do you mean by "visualize urban maps"? Something like this? http://leafletjs.com/examples/choropleth.html
Something like this one: http://img23.imageshack.us/img23/9872/planparcialprovidencia.jpg it's partial plans used for urban development.

1. You can use Google visualization API to show a certain area of a map
https://code.google.com/apis/ajax/playground/?type=visualization#geo_map

2. You can customize the look & feel of GMaps. This is a tool which will help you http://googlemapbuilder.mynameisdonald.com/
